# SOS Project AI Rules (Quick Reference)

## NEVER
- Assume library exports exist
- Use context.session in loaders  
- Use ggt deploy (broken)
- Make multiple changes without testing
- Create files unless absolutely necessary

## ALWAYS  
- Verify imports with grep first
- Test after EVERY change
- Use simple loaders for demos
- Check logs for "Pushed file"
- Keep ggt dev running

## ICONS (Polaris v9)
- End with "Icon" suffix
- No "Major/Minor" suffixes
- TeamIcon NOT CustomersMajor
- ChartLineIcon NOT AnalyticsMajor

## QUICK FIXES
```bash
# Wrong icon? Find correct name:
grep -h "Icon.*from.*polaris" web/routes/*.tsx

# 500 error? Check logs:
tail -20 /tmp/ggt-dev.log | grep ERROR

# Not syncing? Restart:
pkill -f ggt && ./scripts/dev-start.sh
```

